Subject: [PATCH 3/6] phase-0(pr3): services/control_plane FastAPI skeleton

Brings up the v2 control plane: identity, auth, feature flags, system
config, audit, and health probes against an async SQLAlchemy + asyncpg
engine. All state-changing routes emit canonical audit events and the
error envelope matches docs/blueprint/reference/API_SURFACE.md.

Highlights:
- app/{config,db,security,deps,errors,middleware,logging,audit,main}.py
- app/models.py: users, refresh_tokens, feature_flags, system_config,
  audit_log, api_keys, rate_limit_bucket
- app/routes/{health,auth,flags,system_config,audit}.py
- alembic/env.py + 20260419_0001_phase0_baseline.py covering all 7 tables
- app/scripts/seed_bootstrap.py: idempotent admin user, KNOWN_FLAGS
  defaults (kill_switch ON), risk + calibration sentinels
- tests/: aiosqlite-backed coverage for health, auth round-trip, flag
  admin, error envelope, settings validator
- pyproject.toml: aiosqlite dev dep + pytest asyncio-auto config

Deterministic safety floor (Decision #4) is wired: execution.kill_switch
seeds enabled and execution.allow_live + intelligence.allow_autonomous
both seed disabled.

